{"type": "article", "id": 11916, "title": "Balenciaga 2015 秋冬", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-10T11:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000131p0CHiAZFUnRLf7s4.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tBalenciaga 近日发布了 2015 年秋冬广告大片，Kate Moss 和 Lara Stone 出镜。这一季度秋冬主题为“当代传承”。王大仁把他的前卫现代和 Balenciaga 的传统结合，把这一季的核心向珠宝，胸针等方向倾斜，Haute Couture 感无处不在。在手袋上，云石纹的设计仍然看上去很令人惊艳；新的 BAL 58 手袋用来纪念 Cristobal Balenciaga 在 1958 被授予的荣誉骑士勋章； Cable 手袋的 Color Block 拼色看上去活泼靓丽。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135904PlF1LJ6etV49UXA0.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"634\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261359053JFewQ8StdAC1sKB.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135906OWRuUg7tc5EbJpnX.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"621\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261359072Fp4VWKU9fhB5glm.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}